Hello English learners, welcome back to another great podcast here at EnglishPod.
英语学习者你们好，欢迎回到 EnglishPod 的另一期精彩播客。

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:08,000
My name is Marco.
我是 Marco。

3
